    <title>🟣  Start Your Journey with Low-Code/No-Code Development</title>
    <updated>2023-08-29T06:56:25.105000+02:00</updated>
    <author>
      <name>eshrinivasan</name>
      <uri>https://community.sap.com/t5/user/viewprofilepage/user-id/148298</uri>
    </author>
    <content>&lt;P&gt;&lt;SPAN class=""&gt;&lt;SPAN class=""&gt;Have you heard of SAPs definitive low-code tools, for building apps, processes, and business web sites? Do you want to get started using them, and understanding how you make the most of them? Learn how the tools work together, who they're for, and what you can QUICKLY build with them. We'll also review the roadmap for SAP Build for the coming year.&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;</content>
    <link href="https://community.sap.com/t5/devtoberfest/start-your-journey-with-low-code-no-code-development/ev-p/282788"/>
    <published>2023-08-29T06:56:25.105000+02:00</published>
  </entry>
  <entry>
