    <title>🟣 Build S/4HANA Extensions with SAP Build Apps and Key User Extensibility</title>
    <updated>2023-09-06T11:15:48.611000+02:00</updated>
    <author>
      <name>eshrinivasan</name>
      <uri>https://community.sap.com/t5/user/viewprofilepage/user-id/148298</uri>
    </author>
    <content>&lt;P&gt;&lt;SPAN class=""&gt;&lt;SPAN class=""&gt;Join this session to learn how to &lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN class=""&gt;maintain&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN class=""&gt; a clean core and understand the importance of &lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN class=""&gt;&lt;SPAN class=""&gt;extensibility. Dive into the low-code world of SAP Build Apps and SAP S/4 HANA Key user &lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN class=""&gt;&lt;SPAN class=""&gt;extensibility, create and deploy extension applications, and connect your SAP S/4HANA to the SAP BTP seamlessly. With real-world examples and practical exercises, &lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN class=""&gt;you'll&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN class=""&gt; experience firsthand how SAP's low-code tooling can address your business &lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN class=""&gt;challenges.&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;</content>
    <link href="https://community.sap.com/t5/devtoberfest/build-s-4hana-extensions-with-sap-build-apps-and-key-user-extensibility/ev-p/284701"/>
    <published>2023-09-06T11:15:48.611000+02:00</published>
